Brenda Aisaki (愛崎 ブレンダ, Aisaki Burenda) is a character in the series Henjin no Salad Bowl.



Advertisement
Appearance
She looks like a child but is actually 34 years old. She has long red hair and blue eyes.


Advertisement
Personality
Background
Brenda is a 34 year old lawyer who often works with Sōsuke Kaburaya. She is in love with Sōsuke.

Relationships
Sōsuke Kaburaya
A 29-year-old private detective who she often works with and sends clients his way. She is in love with him.

Tateyama
She is Brenda's assistant.

Haruka Neya
They become good friends without knowing that they are both in love with Sōsuke.

Gallery
Trivia
She spent over $3,000 (¥478,000) in the process of making chocolate for Valentine's Day.
Etymology
The name Brenda "sword", "blade of the sword/flaming sword" means in English.
The overall accepted origin for the female name Brenda is the Old Nordic male name Brandr.
Brenda's surname Aisaki means "love, affection" (愛) (ai) and "cape, peninsula" (崎) (saki).
